resources.string: This application has been developed by students of the University of the Basque Country (Alain Alaña, Ana Garaitagoitia, Alazne Hernández, Oier Melsio and Garazi Siara) and CIFP Txurdinaga (Mikel Ayala, Gonzalo Alonso and Josu Morán) in order to help the EP teachers and their students to get to know Santurtzi through didactic games so that they learn while having fun.
